\u00e2m Ng\u1ecd 1942 &amp; Qu\u00fd M\u00f9i 1943, \u00a0Canh D\u1ea7n 1950 &amp; T\u00e2n M\u00e3o 1951, \u00a0M\u1eadu Tu\u1ea5t 1958 &amp; K\u1ef7 H\u1ee3i 1959, \u00a0Nh\u00e2m T\u00fd 1972 &amp; Qu\u00fd S\u1eedu 1973, \u00a0Canh Th\u00e2n 1980 &amp; T\u00e2n D\u1eadu 1981, \u00a0M\u1eadu Th\u00ecn 1988 &amp; K\u1ef7 T\u1ef5 1989.)<\/p>\n<p><a class=\"fancybox\" title=\"\" href=\"http:\/\/toyota.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/09\/chon-mau-xe-o-to-theo-menh-ngu-hanh-va-nam-sinh-388-13.jpg\" rel=\"gallery\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"lazyautosizes lazyloaded\" src=\"http:\/\/toyota.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/09\/chon-mau-xe-o-to-theo-menh-ngu-hanh-va-nam-sinh-388-13.jpg\" sizes=\"689px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/toyota.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/09\/chon-mau-xe-o-to-theo-menh-ngu-hanh-va-nam-sinh-388-13.jpg 480w, http:\/\/toyota.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/09\/chon-mau-xe-o-to-theo-menh-ngu-hanh-va-nam-sinh-388-13.jpg 640w, http:\/\/toyota.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/09\/chon-mau-xe-o-to-theo-menh-ngu-hanh-va-nam-sinh-388-13.jpg 800w, http:\/\/toyota.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/09\/chon-mau-xe-o-to-theo-menh-ngu-hanh-va-nam-sinh-388-13.jpg 1280w\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" data-srcset=\"http:\/\/toyota.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/09\/chon-mau-xe-o-to-theo-menh-ngu-hanh-va-nam-sinh-388-13.jpg 480w, http:\/\/toyota.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/09\/chon-mau-xe-o-to-theo-menh-ngu-hanh-va-nam-sinh-388-13.jpg 640w, http:\/\/toyota.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/09\/chon-mau-xe-o-to-theo-menh-ngu-hanh-va-nam-sinh-388-13.jpg 800w, http:\/\/toyota.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/09\/chon-mau-xe-o-to-theo-menh-ngu-hanh-va-nam-sinh-388-13.jpg 1280w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-optimumx=\"1.6\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>V\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ec7nh M\u1ed9c h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi xe m\u00e0u xanh n\u01b0\u1edbc bi\u1ec3n, \u0111en.<\/p>\n<p>Nh\u00ecn chung, n\u00ean r\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c m\u00e0u t\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1eafc v\u1edbi m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 an t\u00e2m khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng xe. D\u00f9 sao, quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n v\u1eabn l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp trung khi l\u00e1i xe, kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u bia v\u00e0 l\u00e1i xe \u0111\u00fang lu\u1eadt, c\u00f2n n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u00ec d\u00f9 c\u00f3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng xe c\u00f3 m\u00e0u ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ea5y b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc.<\/p>\n<p>Ch\u00fac b\u1ea1n l\u00e1i xe an to\u00e0n.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng, vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u xe ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfc xe g\u1eb7p \u00edt tr\u1ee5c tr\u1eb7c h\u01a1n v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y may m\u1eafn, an to\u00e0n h\u01a1n khi tham gia giao th\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00e3 t\u1eeb l\u00e2u vi\u1ec7c c\u01b0\u1edbi h\u1ecfi, x\u00e2y nh\u00e0, s\u01a1n nh\u00e0 hay mua s\u1eafm \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ea1c d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o &#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":405,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[17],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/toyota.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/388"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/toyota.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/toyota.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/toyota.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/toyota.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=388"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/toyota.webtudong8giay.com\/